{"lemma":"خالِصَةٍ","slug":"خالِصَةٍ","root":"خ.ل.ص","root_slug":"خ-ل-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ل-ص","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"خالِص","root":"خلص","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11267","n11283"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%90%D8%B5%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"pure, unmixed"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"clear"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"sincere, true","examples":[{"text":"لَكَ خَالِصُ الشُّكْرِ","english":"My sincere gratitude"}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"free (from), exempt, liberated"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the best of a thing, essence, extract"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of خَلَصَ (ḵalaṣa, “to be pure, to be clear, to be free from”)."},"ipa":["/xaː.lisˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11267","headword_ar":"خَالصهُ","root":"xlS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxaAlaSapN","text_ar":"مُخَالَصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,) (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He regarded him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acted towards him, with reciprocal purity of mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sincerity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and particularly, as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xAlShu Alwud~a","text_ar":"خالصهُ الوُدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", mentioned in this art. in the A, but not explained,] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he regarded him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acted towards him, with reciprocal purity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sincerity, of love,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affection;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAfaAhu","text_ar":"صَافَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAdadahu","text_ar":"وَادَدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlEi$orapi","text_ar":"فِى العِشْرَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in social intercourse"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xAlS A@ll~`ha","text_ar":"خالص ا@للّٰهَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diynahu","text_ar":"دِينَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He acted with reciprocal purity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sincerity, towards God, in his religion"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAliSi Almuw^omina wa xaAlifi AlkaAfira","text_ar":"خَالِصِ المُوْمِنَ وَ خَالِفِ الكَافِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Act thou with reciprocal purity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sincerity, towards the believer, and act thou with contrariety to the unbeliever"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A. [See 3 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xlq","text_ar":"خلق"},{"kind":"text","text":", where a similar saying is mentioned.]) [See also the next paragraph.]"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TK","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n11283","headword_ar":"خَالِصَةٌ","root":"xlS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAliSN","text_ar":"خَالِصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": used as a subst.,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pure property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quality."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in xxxviii. 46; and K. [In the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xul~ap","text_ar":"خُلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xal~ap","text_ar":"خَلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":": the corresponding word in Bd is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSolap","text_ar":"خَصْلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"},{"kind":"page_break","n":787},{"kind":"text","text":"So in the Kur [xxxviii. 46],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bixaAliSapK","text_ar":"بِخَالِصَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axolaSonaAhumo","text_ar":"اَخْلَصْنَاهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ikoraY Ald~aAri","text_ar":"ذِكْرَى الدَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We have rendered them pure by a pure quality,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd, K, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the keeping in memory the final abode:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd, TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*krY AldAr","text_ar":"ذكرى الدار"},{"kind":"text","text":"being a substitute for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xAlSp","text_ar":"خالصة"},{"kind":"text","text":": or it may mean ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by"},{"kind":"text","text":"] their"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"keeping in memory much the final abode"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the return to God: (TA:) some also, (TA,) namely Náfi' and Hishám, (Bd,) read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bixaAliSapi","text_ar":"بِخَالِصَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", making it a prefix to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*krY","text_ar":"ذكرى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd, TA) as an explicative; or an inf. n., in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwS","text_ar":"خُلُوص"},{"kind":"text","text":", prefixed to its agent. (Bd.) ―         -b2-  You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA Al$~aYo'u xaAliSapN laka","text_ar":"هٰذَا الشَّىْءُ خَالِصَةٌ لَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This thing is a property of thine:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so in a copy of the S, and so the phrase is written in the TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is a thing purely thine, exclusively of others:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h*A Al$Y' xaAliSapF laka","text_ar":"هذا الشىء خَالِصَةً لَكَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"this thing is particularly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"specially, thine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for thee."},{"kind":"text","text":"(So accord. to other copies of the S, and a copy of the JK.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiloSN","text_ar":"خِلْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAliSapN","text_ar":"خَالِصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ixolaASN","text_ar":"اـِخْلَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in some sense not pointed out: see the latter below; and see also 4]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Bd","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}